Abstract: New York Knicks forward Latrell Sprewell says his relationship with Coach Jeff Van Gundy is much smoother because Sprewell understands his role on team (M)
Snippet: New York Knicks forward Latrell Sprewell says his relationship with Coach Jeff Van Gundy is much smoother because Sprewell understands his role on team (M)
LeadParagraph: The fourth-quarter clock was slipping toward the final two minutes Thursday night as Latrell Sprewell sat on the bench with the patience and contentment of a bird watcher.
